nodes.text: Master Starkeiller (name withheld) co-wrote the backstories of Olana Chion and Silya Shessaun appearing in the Databank, through the What's The Story? feature of Hyperspace.
His alias is Master Starkeiller on StarWars.com, and Starkeiller on TheForce.net. He is also a user on Wookieepedia, where he is known as Starkeiller.
